* The sources of income are:
* 1) Agricultural Income (from the sale of grown crops)
* 2) Livestock Income
* 4) Income from wages, casual & permanent waged employment
* 5) Transfers
* 6) Income from non-agricultural enterprise */


******** Income from Agriculture ********
preserve
